description.content:
Hi.

In the digital landscape of today's business world, every company needs a modern ecommerce website to grow their business. It acts as your virtual sales represented 24 hours a day, seven days a week.


If your business is not on the internet or your site isn't mobile-friendly, is outdated, doesn't convert visitors into leads, or isn't up to your satisfaction, you need Modern and Professional Website Designer Service.


I am Shahzaib Cheema, a Wordpress developer and have developed a number of websites that have satisfied my customers.


What will you get?

  • Decent, Latest and Responsive eCommerce/Business/Educational website.
  • Fully Customizable WordPress site.
  • E-Commerce integration.
  • Images slider.
  • SEO optimized.
  • Optimum performance and good load.
  • Fast delivery.
  • Simple/Variable/Digital product upload.
  • Safe & Secure.


Steps in completion of the project.

  1. I will design a website on your requirement.
  2. Show you design, On approval of the design, we will proceed further.
  3. After approval, I will add functionalities.
  4. After adding functionalities, You can ask for revision until satisfaction.


I will show you demo sites according to your requirement.


Order Now! Get the work done.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Requirement to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
1. Domain and Hosting with Cpanel.
2. Logo for your website.
3. Paragraph for About Us Page.
4. List of services you provide with details.
5.Business Email.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I able to edit my website.
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, That is what WordPress is known for.
Anyone can do changing, having a little bit of knowledge.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What are your working hours?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I am available almost all the time, as I have an APP to respond quickly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Shall i place an order or sent a message?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To avoid any confusion, I would request to send me a message before placing an order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I don't know about domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The domain is basically your business name. Hosting is server where we develop and run the website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I don't know, how to buy domain and hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Just leave a message and I will guide you how to get domain and hosting

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain and hosting in your package?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, Domain and hosting will be purchased by you. I want you to have full control of your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What type of website do you develop?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can develop any type of website as you require.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer support after completion of website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide lifetime support to my customer.
